00:01:48.530 --> 00:01:51.490
OK, I'm going to pick
them up from the

00:01:51.490 --> 00:01:54.750
viewer's right to left.

00:01:54.750 --> 00:01:57.120
And what people tend to do is
they do this tedious counting

00:01:57.120 --> 00:01:57.690
out each time.

00:01:57.690 --> 00:02:00.000
And what I'm actually
doing is last time I

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:01.750
